short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Fetch and display LeetCode user stats

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Unlock the power of data with the LeetCode Stats Viewer! This handy Chrome/Edge extension allows you to quickly and easily view comprehensive statistics for any LeetCode user. Whether you're a competitive programmer, a coding enthusiast, or just curious about your progress, LeetCode Stats Viewer provides you with all the insights you need in one convenient place.
